snippet: Kelsey Plumb scored 23 points with eight rebounds and eight assists and broke the school 3-point record, leading No. 11 Washington to an 87-36 win over Savannah State on Sunday for its eighth-straight win....
lead_paragraph: Kelsey Plumb scored 23 points with eight rebounds and eight assists and broke the school 3-point record, leading No. 11 Washington to an 87-36 win over Savannah State on Sunday for its eighth-straight win.

headline.main: Plum Has 23, No. 11 Washington Women Roll Savannah St 87-36
